com.navis.framework.portal.query

Class NullDataQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.navis.framework.portal.query.AbstractDataQuery
      • com.navis.framework.portal.query.NullDataQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataQuery, BasicQuery, Bounded, ExecutableQuery, Ordered, java.io.Serializable

    public class NullDataQuery
extends AbstractDataQuery
    This class represents a DataQuery that can be used in situations where a query is required but it should always return an empty ResultSet. This class follows Fowler's Null Object Pattern which avoids annoying and error-prone null checks.
    Author:
    Etienne Studer
